name: ABBYS (Always Be By Your Side)
description:
Working alone might be unsettling to some. Worry not, I am here to keep you company and bring peace to your surroundings.

As an African Proverb says, "If you want to go fast, go alone. If you want to go far, go together". But why not go fast whilst being together? that's what I'm here for! So you can go fast walking alone, and go far cause you know that I'll always be by your side!
